<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>初心如磐战疫情 使命必达保通信</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>田野坚守在平凡岗位上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诠释初心和使命</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为重庆通信行业争得了荣誉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="//p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201021/06b0367ab29f4a29a7aaf1a72b19d045.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 一场不辞不惧的逆行</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
